edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint2

Class PlanCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.PlanCompiler
      • edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint2.PlanCompiler

  • public class PlanCompiler
extends PlanCompiler
    A translation layer between plan.PlanNode and eval.Operator Extends the plan compiler from checkpoint 1 with support for HashJoins. This is done by overriding compile() and special-casing the new classes of PlanNodes that we wish to handle (Just HashJoinNode in this case). If the node is one of the classes that checkpoint 1 PlanCompiler can handle, we use super.compile() to pass it back up.
